\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

 חוסם את 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

, מתקיים 
\begin_inset Formula $a_{1}\leq x\leq a_{2},b_{1}\leq y\leq b_{2}$
